:+]
.It [+:
  IF (exist? "value")                   :+][+:
    IF (exist? "long-opts")             :+][+:

          # * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
          *
          *  The option has a flag value (character) AND
          *  the program uses long options
