          *
          *  The option has a flag value (character) BUT
          *  the program does _NOT_ use long options
          *
          \:+]
 Fl [+:value:+] [+:
      IF (exist? "arg-type")            :+][+:
            arg-optional Oo     :+] [+:(. opt-arg):+] [+:
            arg-optional Oc     :+] [+:
